function_call.name: get_risks
function_call.arguments: {"risks":[{"Description":"Human movement contributing to the spread of contagious diseases such as malaria.","Impact":"Increased risk of malaria transmission in both source and sink communities.","Mitigation":"Targeting exporter communities with aggressive attack measures and implementing receptivity-lowering activities in importer communities.","Technologies":"Malaria risk connectivity matrices for identifying net exporters and importers, strategic deployment of interventions.","People":"Residents, visitors, communities in northern Namibia.","Owner":"Health authorities, local government, community organizations."}]}
